OL,3,CFarmer jailed after 450 animals
OL,4,Crescued from 'abhorrent conditions'
OL,6,FA farm owner has been jailed and
OL,7,Fbanned from keeping animals for life
OL,8,Fafter more than 450 neglected animals
OL,9,Fwere rescued by the RSPCA.
OL,11,FLee Hayes was handed a 12-month prison
OL,12,Fsentence after a judge heard
OL,13,F"harrowing" evidence of "deliberate
OL,14,Fand sustained" neglect of animals on
OL,15,Fthe Croftfield Farm in Dawgates Lane,
OL,16,FSkegby, near Sutton-in-Ashfield.
