OL,3,CFarmer jailed after 450 animals
OL,4,Crescued from 'abhorrent conditions'
OL,6,FThe RSPCA said dogs, horses,
OL,7,Flivestock, exotic breeds and small
OL,8,Fpets were among the animals found in
OL,9,Fpoor health in what it said was one of
OL,10,Fits biggest ever investigations.
OL,12,FSeveral had to be put to sleep.
OL,14,FHayes, 52, pleaded guilty to 25
OL,15,Foffences under the Animal Welfare Act
OL,16,Fat Mansfield Magistrates' Court.
