OL,3,CFarmer jailed after 450 animals
OL,4,Crescued from 'abhorrent conditions'
OL,6,FDistrict Judge Grace Leong told him:
OL,7,F"All the animals were still living in
OL,8,Fabhorrent conditions and severely
OL,9,Fneglected, which included unsanitary,
OL,10,Fovercrowded accommodation, dogs living
OL,11,Fin faeces and urine, goats with
OL,12,Fovergrown hooves, equines with thrush
OL,13,Fand cats with fleas and flu.
OL,15,F"A lot of this could easily have been
OL,16,Fprevented, but you wantonly neglected
OL,17,Fhundreds of animals of a wide range of
OL,18,Fspecies."
