OL,3,CFarmer jailed after 450 animals
OL,4,Crescued from 'abhorrent conditions'
OL,6,FHayes' girlfriend, Tammy Heath, 33, of
OL,7,FMoorland Close, Skegby, pleaded guilty
OL,8,Fto two animal welfare offences and was
OL,9,Fgiven a 13-week prison sentence,
OL,10,Fsuspended for 12 months. She was
OL,11,Fbanned from keeping dogs for five
OL,12,Fyears.
OL,14,FConcerns about neglect were first
OL,15,Fraised after a missing dogs' charity
OL,16,Fvisited the farm in 2023 to
OL,17,Finvestigate claims about a stolen dog.
