OL,3,CFarmer jailed after 450 animals
OL,4,Crescued from 'abhorrent conditions'
OL,6,FNottinghamshire Police were called and
OL,7,Ffound a barn housing dogs who were
OL,8,Fwhining. Some were eating their own
OL,9,Ffaeces. Hayes was reported to the
OL,10,FRSPCA.
OL,12,FThe RSPCA's officers raided the farm
OL,13,Fwith Nottinghamshire Police on 1
OL,14,FNovember 2023.
OL,16,FAmong the most severely neglected
OL,17,Fanimals was a German shepherd dog,
OL,18,Ftethered to a small kennel and
OL,19,Fstruggling to walk.
