OL,3,CFarmer jailed after 450 animals
OL,4,Crescued from 'abhorrent conditions'
OL,6,FThe officers also found a cocker
OL,7,Fspaniel, who later needed hernia
OL,8,Fsurgery.
OL,10,FDonkeys and horses were suffering from
OL,11,Frotting feet without attention from a
OL,12,Fvet or a farrier. Some were
OL,13,Funderweight and others had not
OL,14,Freceived any treatment for parasites
OL,15,Fand proper dental care.
OL,17,FThere were more than 40 dogs living in
OL,18,Fkennels in a dark barn.
