OL,3,CFarmer jailed after 450 animals
OL,4,Crescued from 'abhorrent conditions'
OL,6,FHayes had claimed that circumstances
OL,7,Fat the farm had "all got a little out
OL,8,Fof hand", but the district judge said
OL,9,Fthe defendant ignored previous
OL,10,Fwarnings to make welfare improvements.
OL,12,FRSPCA Inspector Baker, who led the
OL,13,Foperation, said: "The conditions we
OL,14,Ffound all these animals living in were
OL,15,Fabsolutely appalling. The smell of
OL,16,Fmanure hit as soon as you walked
OL,17,Fthrough the gate and the sheer volume
OL,18,Fof animals in dire circumstances was
OL,19,Fquite overwhelming."
